description: Testing expectations and reproducibility guardrails
globs: ["pipelines/**/*.py", "scripts/**/*.py", "tests/**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- When you change LiDAR pipeline logic or parameters, ensure the golden AOI guardrail remains valid (`tests/test_golden_aoi.py`).
- Prefer adding/regenerating regression tests when you change file schemas, paths, or parameter defaults.
- Keep tests deterministic: fixed seeds, stable ordering, and avoid reliance on local machine state.
